Open Postman
To Register User:-
 POST :-http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/acount/register/
To Login User:-
POST :-http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/acount/login/
Copy the access token and add it to the authorization


To Create a blog:
POST- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/home/blog/

Add Form data-
https://prnt.sc/jDXD65FF-mqj

To Search a Blog:
GET--http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/home/blog/?search=[blog title]


To Update a blog:
PATCH-http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/home/blog/?search=The bLog title
https://prnt.sc/vKQQx2FM0uJ_

To Delete a blog:
DELETE-http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/home/blog/?search=The bLog title
https://prnt.sc/PASDelmgJ7FS

